span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:1.5;font-family:宋体;color:black\">元整，具体详见招标文件。</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"margin:0cm;margin-bottom:.0001pt;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;font-size:10.5pt;font-family:\'Times New Roman\',\'serif\';text-indent:24.0pt;line-height:1.5;layout-grid-mode:\r\nchar;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric\"><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;\r\nline-height:1.5;font-family:宋体;color:black\">五、评标办法</span><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:1.5;color:black\">:</span><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:1.5;font-family:宋体;color:black\">本项目采用“竞争性谈判”法，具体详见招标文件。</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"margin:0cm;margin-bottom:.0001pt;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;font-size:10.5pt;font-family:\'Times New Roman\',\'serif\';text-indent:24.0pt;line-height:1.5;layout-grid-mode:\r\nchar;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric\"><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;\r\nline-height:1.5;font-family:宋体;color:black\">六、招标文件领取：</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"margin:0cm;margin-bottom:.0001pt;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;font-size:10.5pt;font-family:\'Times New Roman\',\'serif\';text-indent:24.0pt;line-height:1.5;layout-grid-mode:\r\nchar;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric\"><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;\r\nline-height:1.5;font-family:宋体;color:black\">投标报名及竞争性谈判文件的获取，请符合上述资质条件的投标人携带单位介绍信</span><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:1.5;color:black\">(</span><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:1.5;font-family:宋体;color:black\">或授权委托书，须注明联系人、电话及邮箱</span><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:1.5;color:black\">)</span><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:1.5;font-family:宋体;color:black\">原件到</span><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:1.5;font-family:宋体;color:black\">江苏全盛工程造价事务所有限公司</span><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:1.5;color:black\">(</span><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:1.5;font-family:宋体;color:black\">盐城市解放南路</span><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:1.5;color:black\">199</span>