ograph;text-indent:20.95pt;line-height:17.55pt;font-size:10.5pt;font-family:\'Times New Roman\',\'serif\';color:black;text-align:left;text-indent:24.0pt;\r\nline-height:1.5\" align=\"left\"><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:1.5;\r\nfont-family:宋体;background:white\">2.</span><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;\r\nline-height:1.5;font-family:宋体;background:white\">项目地点：盐城市第一人民医院</span><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:1.5;font-family:宋体;color:windowtext;\r\nbackground:white\">。</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"margin:0cm;margin-bottom:.0001pt;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;text-indent:20.95pt;line-height:17.55pt;font-size:10.5pt;font-family:\'Times New Roman\',\'serif\';color:black;text-align:left;text-indent:24.0pt;\r\nline-height:1.5\" align=\"left\"><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:1.5;\r\nfont-family:宋体;background:white\">3.</span><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;\r\nline-height:1.5;font-family:宋体;color:windowtext\">项目内容：盐城市第一人民医院主院区方仓<span>CT</span>设备机预评价、控制效果评价和环评服务，包括但不限于：</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"margin:0cm;margin-bottom:.0001pt;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;text-indent:20.95pt;line-height:17.55pt;font-size:10.5pt;font-family:\'Times New Roman\',\'serif\';color:black;text-align:left;text-indent:24.0pt;\r\nline-height:1.5\" align=\"left\"><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:1.5;font-family:\r\n宋体;color:windowtext\">（</span><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;\r\nline-height:1.5;font-family:宋体;background:white\">1</span><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:1.5;font-family:宋体;background:white\">）卫生：放射诊疗设备预评价和控制效果评价（含批复）、办理放射诊疗许可证；</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"margin:0cm;margin-bottom:.0001pt;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;text-indent:20.95pt;line-height:17.55pt;font-size:10.5pt;font-family:\'Times New Roman\',\'serif\';color:black;text-align:left;text-indent:24.0pt;\r\nline-height:1.5\" align=\"left\"><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:1.5;font-family:\r\n宋体;background:white\">（<span>2</